<h2>
  <a id=Search_15626900281916867_13804_7288827267039479 name=Search_15626900281916867_13804_7288827267039479></a>Search
</h2>
<a href=http://loc.gov/pictures/search/?q=%3Cquery%3E&amp;fo=json id=hxvc title="https://loc.gov/pictures/search/?q=<query>&amp;fo=json">http://loc.gov/pictures/search/?q=&lt;query&gt;&amp;fo=json</a><br>
<br>
Searches descriptive information for the search terms specified by &lt;query&gt;.<br>
<h3>
  <a id=Options_992118639962267_176292_7192582657780896 name=Options_992118639962267_176292_7192582657780896></a>Options
</h3>
<b><font face="Courier New">Search Options<br>
</font></b>
<div style=MARGIN-LEFT:40px>
  <b><font face="Courier New">q </font></b><font face="Courier New">- query, search terms (None)</font><br>
</div>
<div style=MARGIN-LEFT:40px>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>fa</b> - facets, format = &lt;field&gt;|&lt;facet value&gt; (None)</font><br>
</div>
<div style=MARGIN-LEFT:40px>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>co</b> - collection (None)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>co!</b> - _not_ collection (None)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>op</b> - operator (AND)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>va</b> - variants, (True)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>fi</b> - fields (None/"text")</font><br>
</div>
<font face="Courier New"><b><br>
Results Options<br>
</b></font>
<div style=MARGIN-LEFT:40px>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>c</b> - count (20)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>st</b> - style, (list)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>sp</b> - start page, (1)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>si</b> - start index (1)</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>fo</b> - format</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"><b>sb</b> - sort by (relevance)</font><br>
</div>
<br>
