  <a id=Response_6677025663268493_2053_40533640032747453 name=Response_6677025663268493_2053_40533640032747453></a>Response
</h3>
All links provided by the resources link property provide the same resources, collection, and indexes properties, but the essay property will contain the html content for the specified collection resource.<br>
<h4>
  <a id=_collection_7971473457006178_3_012643777289184976 name=_collection_7971473457006178_3_012643777289184976></a><font face="Courier New">"collection"</font>
</h4>
<blockquote>
  <font face="Courier New">{</font><br>
  <font face="Courier New"> &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;"<b>code</b>": "ecur", </font><br>
